snippet.title: Vox Stoica
snippet.description:
I record audiobooks, mostly on Stoicism. All my work is my own and I maintain the copyright to it. If you wish to use any clips of them for some creative purpose just drop me a message.
You can buy my recordings on Audible: https://geni.us/VoxStoicaOnAudible
You can also get mp3s of all my recordings by becoming a patron:  https://www.patreon.com/RobinHomer | https://www.subscribestar.com/intpworld 
I live in London, UK
